    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint still holds a deep shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper corner. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
