      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and still has tons of life left in it! It drives like a dream and is perfect for anyone looking for a reliable, comfy car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve loved every mile in this beauty, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
