      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish with only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is supple and free of significant wear, while all electronic features, premium audio, and climate controls function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, benefiting from a documented history of preventative maintenance and timely fluid changes. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, confident ride with plenty of life left in the tires and brakes. Whether you are looking for a reliable commuter or a weekend tourer, this car is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 35500.0,
